      <title>内塔尼亚胡称与哈马斯达成人质协议的前景正在改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/netanyahu-says-prospects-for-a-hostage-deal-with-hamas-improving</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡表示，与哈马斯达成停火和人质协议的条件“正逐渐成熟”，这表明双方越来越接近同意至少暂时停止在加沙的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/netanyahu-says-prospects-for-a-hostage-deal-with-hamas-improving</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 09:24:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯开始竞选，必须自己制定如何击败特朗普的方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/harris-hits-trail-having-to-make-her-own-how-to-beat-trump-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯将于周二在密尔沃基举行集会，正式启动她刚刚开始的总统竞选活动，试图回答民主党人心中最关心的问题：她打算如何击败唐纳德·特朗普？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/harris-hits-trail-having-to-make-her-own-how-to-beat-trump-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
