      <title>印度削减黄金进口税以促进本土珠宝制造商发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/india-cuts-gold-import-tax-in-boost-to-local-jewelry-makers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度削减了黄金进口税，以支持全球第二大贵金属消费国的珠宝制造业。]]></description>
